Andfun Yangon/Studio

Version: 1.0

Features Developed: 
    Web cam capturing 3 imgaes per second automatically.


Version: 2.0

New Features: 
    Multiple Web cam capturing 3 imgaes per second automatically.

Description:
    I set the limit of auto capturing imgaes just to 20 phtots.

Usage:
    "auto_capture_config.txt" is input for user's desired setting.
    "auto_capture.py" will do the main function.
    "usbVideoDevice.py" is class for retrieval of device id & port number.
    "index.py" is to get connected device id and port.

    
Requirement:
    pip install opencv-python numpy

How to run:
    python auto_capture.py

